OL,7,FA man who stabbed the manager of a
OL,8,FBallymena hostel 55 times was on
OL,9,FFriday informed he will spend a
OL,10,Fminimum of 20 years in jail for the
OL,11,F"brutal" murder.
OL,13,FInayat Shah, 67, who ran the
OL,14,FTraveller's Rest on the Galgorm Road
OL,15,Fin the Co Antrim town, was murdered by
OL,16,FMichael Lenaghan on the afternoon of
OL,17,F21 March 2020.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G1/13
