OL,7,FMr Shah provided accommodation for
OL,8,Fpeople who found themselves homeless,
OL,9,Ffor those who had just been released
OL,10,Ffrom prison and for people with
OL,11,Fcomplex needs.
OL,13,FLenaghan was one such resident and as
OL,14,Fshe imposed the sentence upon him,
OL,15,FJudge Patricia Smyth said: "Mr Shah
OL,16,Fprovided a valuable public service and
OL,17,Fit cost him his life."
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G2/13
