OL,7,FAs relatives of Mr Shah sat in the
OL,8,Fpublic gallery of Belfast Crown Court,
OL,9,FJudge Smyth paid tribute to him and
OL,10,Fspoke of the loss his death has had on
OL,11,Fhis loved ones.
OL,13,FThe court heard that on the afternoon
OL,14,Fof 21 March 2020, Lenaghan - who at
OL,15,Fthe time had been living in a self-
OL,16,Fcontained flat in the Travellers Rest
OL,17,F- threatened to kill a resident.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G3/13
