OL,7,FHe then stabbed another resident in
OL,8,Fthe chest who made his way to Mr
OL,9,FShah's living quarters to get
OL,10,Fassistance.
OL,12,FThe wounded man then left the
OL,13,Fproperly, followed by Mr Shah, who at
OL,14,Fthis stage was on the phone with the
OL,15,Femergency services.
OL,17,FAs they made their way to Lenaghan's
OL,18,Faccommodation, he approached them
OL,19,Faggressively whilst carrying the knife.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G4/13
