OL,7,FMr Shah started to run from the armed
OL,8,Fman, but he slipped on the ground and
OL,9,Fwas then stabbed repeatedly by
OL,10,FLenaghan.
OL,12,FAs Mr Shah was still on the phone, the
OL,13,Fentire attack was recorded on the 999
OL,14,Fcall in what Judge Smyth described as
OL,15,F"in harrowing detail."
OL,17,FShe said Mr Shah's "repeated screams"
OL,18,Fcan be heard along with him offering
OL,19,Fmoney to Lenaghan in return for his
OL,20,Flife.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G5/13
