OL,7,FHe told the resident he threatened
OL,8,Fearlier that day 'you'll end up like
OL,9,FShah there, dead in the street.'
OL,11,FA short time later, Lenaghan was
OL,12,Fapproached by police and said 'that
OL,13,Fthing is in the alley. I did it. It's
OL,14,Fme you're looking for.'
OL,16,FWhen arrested for murder, Lenaghan
OL,17,Fasked 'is he dead?' and when told this
OL,18,Fwas the case, he replied 'f*****g
OL,19,Fgood'. He was overheard by Mr Shah's
OL,20,Fdaughter shouting 'happy days.'
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G7/13
