OL,7,FHe was aggressive and abusive to
OL,8,Fofficers and to custody staff at the
OL,9,FPSNI station.
OL,11,FDuring a police interview, he gave a
OL,12,Flargely 'no comment' response - but
OL,13,Fsubsequently pleaded guilty to charges
OL,14,Fof murdering Mr Shah, wounding one
OL,15,Ffellow resident and threatening to
OL,16,Fkill a second.
OL,18,FHe said he felt Mr Shah was a 'tout'
OL,19,Fand was trying to get him sent back to
OL,20,Fprison.
