OL,7,FDuring Friday's Tariff hearing, the
OL,8,FBelfast Recorder noted Lenaghan's
OL,9,F"relevant" criminal record consisting
OL,10,Fof over 130 offences as well as his
OL,11,Fconsumption of alcohol and drugs prior
OL,12,Fto the murder.
OL,14,FShe also noted that medical experts
OL,15,Fagreed that he was suffering from an
OL,16,Fabnormality of mental functioning at
OL,17,Fthe time.
OL,19,FJudge Smyth said she had read
OL,20,Fstatements provided by Mr Shah's loved
OL,21,Fones.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G9/13
