OL,7,FThe deceased man's daughter spoke of
OL,8,Fher loss, grief and depression since
OL,9,Fher father's death and the "searing
OL,10,Fpain" of his absence.
OL,12,FMr Shah's son spoke of the
OL,13,Fdifficulties he experienced with the
OL,14,Fcourt proceedings and the lack of
OL,15,Fremorse on Lenaghan's part.
OL,17,FHe also described his father as a
OL,18,F"kind, loving and charitable" man who
OL,19,Fwould help anyone in the community.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                         G10/13
