OL,7,FIn his statement, he asked the
OL,8,Fquestion "why was the defendant free
OL,9,Fto commit this terrible crime?"
OL,11,FMr Shah's partner also spoke of his
OL,12,Fgenerosity and said "the people of
OL,13,FBallymena have been robbed of a great
OL,14,Fman."
OL,16,FJudge Smyth said that after receiving
OL,17,Fthese and other statements, it was
OL,18,Fclear he provided a "unique" public
OL,19,Fservice to those with complex needs.
