OL,7,FBranding the fatal knife attack as
OL,8,Fboth "brutal" and "ferocious", Judge
OL,9,FSmyth imposed a minimum term of 20
OL,10,Fyears which Lenaghan must serve before
OL,11,Fhe is considered eligible for release
OL,12,Fby the Parole Commissioners.
OL,14,FHe showed no emotion as the term was
OL,15,Fimposed and was handcuffed then led
OL,16,Ffrom the dock and back into custody by
OL,17,Fprison staff.
